(10, 5, NULL, '2017-07-19', '2017-08-19', 0, 2, 2, 0, 'B.E. Cooling', 'Private Bag X9008', 'Crown Mines', 'Durban', 'KZN', '2025', 192, 'PINETOWN CAPEX - 3025356\n\nOriginal Call Out : CF20034709 - 3025356\nButchery Cold Room - Asset Tag # 3719\n\n22 / 23.06.2017\nJob Card # 01972 / 01973\n\nFound 2 x blower coils iced up.  Defrosted coil, cleaned fan motor and blades.  Cleaned drip trays. Inspected compressor and found the valves are broken.  Compressor needs to be replaced as well as the oil separator.\n\nReturned to site with the necessary spares.  Decommissioned refrigeration plant, removed existing compressor and oil separator, made safe.  Re-installed new compressor and oil separator, evacuated and commissioned system with refrigerant gas.  Checked settings and parameters.', ''),
