(18, 39, NULL, '2017-08-04', '2017-09-04', 0, 1, 2, 0, 'B.E. Cooling', 'P.O. Box 4211, Randburg', '', 'Johannesburg', 'KZN', '2125', 192, 'SASOL AVOCA - 500513497\n\nVENDOR # 12096\n\nCALL OUT : \n21.07.2017 - Deli Chiller\n\nResponded to call out.  Inspected unit and checked refrigerant pressures.  Found unit short of refrigerant.  Leak tested and located leak on the elbows of the coil.  Repaired leak and charged unit with refrigerant that was lost.  \n\nRecommend the cabinet be replaced as this is not the first refrigerant leak to occur.\n\nSCOPE OF WORK:\nTo decommission Upright Cabinet refrigeration plant, disconnect piping, cable and drains and make safe.  Remove 6ft Upright Cabinet out of shop area and transport off site.  To install new cabinet, line up and position into new place.  Connect piping, electrics, cables and drain.  Evacuate plant of any contamination, commission plant with new refrigerant gas.  Check all settings and parameters.', ''),
