(20, 39, NULL, '2017-08-10', '2017-09-10', 0, 1, 2, 0, 'B.E. Cooling', 'P.O. Box 4211, Randburg', '', 'Johannesburg', 'KZN', '2125', 192, 'SASOL STANGER - 500515320\n\nVENDOR # 12096\n\nCALL OUT : 07.08.2017\nOffice aircon tripping.\nResponded to call out.  Found the compressor of the airconditioning unit faulty causing the mains to trip.  Recommend the airconditioning unit be replaced as it is extremely old and crumbling.  Disconnected airconditioning unit from circuit.\n\nSCOPE OF WORK :\nTo decommission existing airconditioning plant and make safe.  Remove existing indoor and outdoor unit.  To re-install new 24 000 btu Mitsubishi indoor and outdoor unit.  Evacuate plant of any contamination, commission plant with new refrigerant gas.  Check all settings and parameters.', ''),
(21, 5, NULL, '2017-08-11', '2017-09-11', 0, 1, 2, 0, 'B.E. Cooling', 'Private Bag X9008', 'Crown Mines', 'Durban', 'KZN', '2025', 192, 'RICHARDS BAY\nCity Job Number : 3026067\n\n24 / 25.07.2017\nJob Card # 01830 / 01663\nMT Rack - Plant Room\n\nResponded to call out.  Found unit short of refrigerant.  Added refrigerant to get temperatures down.  Started with leak checking.  Was unable to locate leak.  Will return the next day to continue.  Returned and continued with leak checking.  Located leak on upright piping.  Repair leak and added refrigerant to MT Rack.', 'Please note : \nOriginal Call Out - CF20034807 - 3025694 has been cancelled due to invite to quote generated.\nMark Barker requested quote to be done as per email from Portal 10.08.2017'),
(22, 39, NULL, '2017-08-21', '2017-09-21', 0, 1, 2, 0, 'B.E. Cooling', 'P.O. Box 4211, Randburg', '', 'Johannesburg', 'KZN', '2125', 192, 'SASOL COWIES HILL\n\nVENDOR # 12096\n\nTO SUPPLY AND INSTALL COMBI CHILLER 6 GLASS DOOR AND FREEZER ROOM 1 GLASS DOOR\n\nSCOPE OF WORK :\n\n*  Combination Cold Room / Freezer Room 6.2 x 1.8 x 2.6m high using polyurethane foam injected panels 75mm thick.  Chequerplate floor with heater mat in Freezer and insulated chequerplate flooring in Chiller.  One std hinged door into Freezer from Chiller Room and one sliding door into Chiller, both with strip curtains.  7 x low temp glass door all with 6 tier shelving. \n\n*  To supply and install Refrigeration Equipment for 6 Glass Door Cold Room :\n   *  1 x Wall Mount Pack\n   *  1 x Blower Coil\n\n*  To supply and install Refrigeration Equipment for 1 Glass Door Freezer Room :\n   *  1 x Wall Mount Pack\n   *  1 x Blower Coil\n\nWall Pack units come complete with the following:\n*  All rises to have P-Traps and every 2.5m Freezers to have 1 inch armeflex, Chillers are to have 3/4 inch armeflex.\n*  All systems to operate on 404A refrigerant\n*  Refrigeration, Piping, Armeflex, Elbows, Couplings, T-Pieces and P-Traps, Welding, Refrigerant, Brackets, Sealant, Sundries, Drains, Heaters for Freezer Rooms, Labour, Travel and Transport', ''),
